data.description: Come see this 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhome located in the highly sought Brook Hills West subdivision. As you enter, you will be immediately impressed with the tall ceilings and abundant light in the living space.  Nicely updated kitchen and baths. Hardwood on main level and carpeted  upstairs. Large basement perfect for entertaining and terrific storage.  Loft space upstairs makes for a perfect additional living space, office or workout room. Wood burning fireplace with brick hearth in living room.  Excellent location close to Orland Park 179th St. Metra and plenty of shopping and restaurants.  Full finished basement with tile flooring. Additional room in basement could be used for an office or sleeping space. Pet-friendly.  Nice deck for your grill and outdoor living. 2-car attached garage so you can stay warm all winter.
